      "description": "Upgrade the backlog and roadmap system to support explicit epic/thematic grouping, dependency mapping, status/ownership, LLM/AI-first metadata, automated hygiene, backlog-to-roadmap sync, contextual enhancement, change history, feedback loop, and automated suggestion/refinement. This will enable a living, actionable, and context-rich backlog always in sync with code, docs, and roadmap.",
